| ''Far Out'' is considered generally unreliable as a [[churnalism]] outlet that appears to engage in [[WP:CIRCULAR|circular sourcing]].
| {{WP:RSPUSES|faroutmagazine.co.uk}}

|- class="s-gu" id="The Federalist"
| data-sort-value="Federalist" | ''[[The Federalist (website)|The Federalist]]'' {{WP:RSPSHORTCUT|WP:THEFEDERALIST}}
| {{WP:RSPSTATUS|gu}}
| {{rsnl|336|RFC: The Federalist|2021|rfc=y}}
| {{WP:RSPLAST|2021}}
