| {{WP:RSPUSES|thefederalist.com}}

|- class="s-gu" id="FilmAffinity"
| [[FilmAffinity]]
| {{WP:RSPSTATUS|gu}}
| [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 229#Film Affinity|1]]<br> [[Wikipedia talk:WikiProject Film/Archive 65#FilmAffinity|A]] [[Wikipedia talk:WikiProject Film/Resources#Filmaffinity|B]] [[Wikipedia talk:WikiProject Film/Archive 67#FilmAffinity revisited|C]]
| {{WP:RSPLAST|2018|stale=n}}
