| {{WP:RSPSTATUS|gr}}
| {{rsnl|293|RfC: The Indian Express|2020|rfc=y}}
| {{WP:RSPLAST|2020}}
| ''The Indian Express'' is considered generally reliable under the [[WP:NEWSORG|news organizations guideline]].
| {{WP:RSPUSES|indianexpress.com}}

