| {{WP:RSPSTATUS|gu|b=y}}
| {{rsnl|301|RfC: Crowdfunders|2020|rfc=y}}
| {{WP:RSPLAST|2020|stale=n}}
| Indiegogo is a [[crowdfunding]] website specializing in funding for start-up charities or businesses. As a primary source, it should usually be avoided for topics involving crowdfunding campaigns where better sources are available. The 2020 RfC gained a consensus for Indiegogo to be placed on the [[WP:SPB|Wikipedia spam blacklist]]; links must be whitelisted before they can be used.
| {{WP:RSPUSES|indiegogo.com}}

|- class="s-gu" id="Indymedia"
| [[Indymedia]] <small>(Independent Media Center, IMC)</small> {{WP:RSPSHORTCUT|WP:IMC}} {{WP:RSPSHORTCUT|WP:INDYMEDIA}}
