| [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 83#Times and IBTimes RS?|1]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 104#International Business Times|2]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 195#Slate, WGN, International Business Times|3]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 218#International Business Times as a reliable source?|4]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 222#International Business Times|5]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 262#International Business Times|6]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 262#Use of blogs for sourcing height in BLPs|7]]
