| {{rsnl|490|RfC: Journal of Scientific Exploration|2025|rfc=y}}<br>
| {{WP:RSPLAST|2025}}
| The ''Journal of Scientific Exploration'' is published by the [[Society for Scientific Exploration]], which has been criticized for advancing fringe ideas. The journal itself has been accused of publishing pseudoscience, including speculative studies presuming the existence of ghosts and magic. 
