| [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 35#encyclopedia.jrank.org and "contributed articles"|1]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 201#http://thedevilanddanvojir.blogspot.ca/2009_07_02_archive.html et al|2]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 214#http://encyclopedia.jrank.org/|3]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 263#https://biography.jrank.org|4]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 368#Jrank.org|5]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 380#Should Jrank.org be deprecated?|6]]
| {{WP:RSPLAST|2022}}
