| {{WP:RSPUSES|jrank.org}}

|- class="s-b" id="Kickstarter"
| [[Kickstarter]] {{WP:RSPSHORTCUT|WP:KICKSTARTER}}
| {{WP:RSPSTATUS|gu|b=y}}
| {{rsnl|301|RfC: Crowdfunders|2020|rfc=y}}
| {{WP:RSPLAST|2020|stale=n}}
| Kickstarter is a [[crowdfunding]] website specializing in funding for new works of fiction. As a primary source, it should usually be avoided for topics involving crowdfunding campaigns where better sources are available. The 2020 RfC gained a consensus for Kickstarter to be placed on the [[WP:SPB|Wikipedia spam blacklist]]; links must be whitelisted before they can be used.
| {{WP:RSPUSES|kickstarter.com}}

|- class="s-gr" id="Kirkus Reviews"
