|- class="s-gu" id="Sixth Tone (politics)"
| ''[[Sixth Tone]]'' (politics)
| {{WP:RSPSTATUS|gu}}
| {{rsnl|287|RfC: Sixth Tone|2020|rfc=y}}
| {{WP:RSPLAST|2020|stale=n}}
