|- class="s-gr" id="Sports Illustrated (pre-June 2019)"
| ''[[Sports Illustrated]]'' (pre–June 2019)
| {{WP:RSPSTATUS|gr}}
| [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 421#Sports Illustrated|1]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 422#RfC: Sports Illustrated|2]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 425#Sports Illustrated...|3]] [[Wikipedia:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 471#Sports Illustrated|4]]
