| [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 168#Stack Overflow a reliable source for an algorithm?|1]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 228#Can the Stack Exchange Network be considered reliable?|2]] [[WP:Reliable sources/Noticeboard/Archive 402#Is Stack Exchange a reliable source|3]]<br> [[Talk:Leap year/Archive 3#RfC: use "peer-reviewed" in connection with stackoverflow.com|A]]
